{"id": 973, "genre": 1001, "title": "在发型这件事上，你有哪些心得？", "description": "纽约时报告诉你，型男应该10天理发一次。（题图来自：John Holcroft）", "record_count": 4245, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152328KzmbCoEwW76uDxpS.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-02T01:00:55Z", "options": [{"id": 73217, "content": "发型很重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579533}, {"id": 73473, "content": "发型衣服鞋子甚至是食物，说白了都是当下的一种心情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480625}, {"id": 73474, "content": "理发师手下叫发型，在自己手里叫头发。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593604}, {"id": 73475, "content": "理发师手下叫发型，自己手里叫头发。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593604}, {"id": 73220, "content": "告诉理发师：剪短", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523916}, {"id": 73476, "content": "直发的人永远无法理解自然卷的痛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 96253}, {"id": 73223, "content": "是不是只有我会丧心病狂每月两次穿越整个城市就为剪个头发", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591350}, {"id": 73479, "content": "整理大家的意见吧，不同是时间段，不同的风格都要适应适应。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591285}, {"id": 73480, "content": "发型理完之后，估计觉得满意的只有理发师了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593234}, {"id": 73225, "content": "头型远比发型好！有个好头型任何发型都能驾驭。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112082}, {"id": 73481, "content": "任何流行的发型到自己头上就是一堆草！！！主要还是看颜值……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593638}, {"id": 73226, "content": "颜值高的，会在意什么叫发型？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 9267}, {"id": 73483, "content": "无论胖瘦，大头让我只有一个发型，衰", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586630}, {"id": 73228, "content": "是个人的展现", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566742}, {"id": 73229, "content": "脏辫两年半的呵呵了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 470645}, {"id": 73485, "content": "开心就好??????????", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593617}, {"id": 73230, "content": "都是时尚的奴隶", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 574784}, {"id": 73486, "content": "今天烫了卷，明天就糊了 打理无能……|墙| ू‾᷄ω‾᷅)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410916}, {"id": 74510, "content": "忽略发型师的任何建议，开启睡神模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595067}, {"id": 73232, "content": "感觉被冒犯了！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592994}, {"id": 73488, "content": "为了发型每天都要洗头，为了不想洗头每天都想把头发剪了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 557035}, {"id": 73234, "content": "理发师永远不懂什么叫做修一修以及“稍微”剪短一点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 83624}, {"id": 73490, "content": "长得好看的人的发型往往都是当季流行的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471871}, {"id": 73235, "content": "主要是脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 587066}, {"id": 73491, "content": "沙发➕自来卷伤不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536591}, {"id": 76563, "content": "及肩长发的尴尬，图片上都是浮云", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602641}, {"id": 73236, "content": "刘海是最难搞的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 470456}, {"id": 73492, "content": "每次理完发都觉得自己被理发师精神强奸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363292}, {"id": 73493, "content": "不要轻易尝试换个发型师", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346803}, {"id": 73238, "content": "发型真的很重要。出门的洗头，居然可能转角遇到男神。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579910}, {"id": 74774, "content": "长的丑，梳什么发型，都丑…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598714}, {"id": 73495, "content": "说看脸的，剃光头也美美哒？哈哈哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 371851}, {"id": 73496, "content": "换发型师试一次赌注", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346803}, {"id": 73752, "content": "我想知道光头的人看到这些会有什么感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 38139}, {"id": 73241, "content": "终究还是看脸型", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257145}, {"id": 73497, "content": "短发久了 不想留长", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578770}, {"id": 73498, "content": "从理发店出来到回家睡觉洗头之前那才算发型", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590254}, {"id": 73246, "content": "感觉还是看脸！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485322}, {"id": 73247, "content": "头型比发型重要多了，头型好，什么发型都可以！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112082}, {"id": 73503, "content": "留头发时候不要照镜子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 24838}, {"id": 73248, "content": "讲真，男的一个月至少剪两次，尤其是短发。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 570356}, {"id": 73249, "content": "第一天披着，第二天扎着，第三天马尾扎半头，第四天用婴儿痱子粉花洒在头顶让其蓬松去油，第五天真的要洗头发了。我的发型大概是这样的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590166}, {"id": 73505, "content": "理发师根本不会在意你的意见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167116}, {"id": 73250, "content": "谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 409739}, {"id": 73506, "content": "看脸才是王道^_～", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593705}, {"id": 73251, "content": "上班前型男，下班后屌丝", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593098}, {"id": 74531, "content": "这个莫名流行短发的时代", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597722}, {"id": 73252, "content": "洗头前和洗头后是两个发型?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 384513}, {"id": 73508, "content": "It doesn't matter！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593708}, {"id": 73509, "content": "It doesn't matter", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593708}]}